OL,5, Amazon founder Jeff Bezos has said he  
OL,6, plans to give away most of his $124bn  
OL,7, (#107bn) fortune during his lifetime.  
OL,9,FThe businessman told news network CNN  
OL,10,Fhe would donate his wealth to fighting 
OL,11,Fclimate change and reducing inequality.
OL,13,FHe has previously been criticised for  
OL,14,Fnot signing up to the Giving Pledge - a
OL,15,Fpromise by some of the world's         
OL,16,Fwealthiest people to dedicate their    
OL,17,Ffortunes to charity.                   
OL,19,FInvestor Warren Buffett and Microsoft  
OL,20,Ffounder Bill Gates have both signed.   
